  "detailed_description": "Take on the role of a blacksmith in the castle, create weapons and sell it to the soldiers , or the army of darkness will capture the last castle , which the darkness has not yet found but closer .<br />\r\n- Early access <br />\r\n- 10 types of weapons. 5 kinds of metal for objects.<br />\r\n- 12 other items to create. <br />\r\n Don't let the oven cool down.<br />\r\n- Buy ore, fuel, food from the merchant.<br />\r\n- Mine the ore yourself outside the castle walls.<br />\r\n- Upgrade ovens-buy parts and assemble boilers.<br />\r\n- Hire a miner to bring you ore.<br />\r\n- Don't forget to sleep , eat , drink.<br />\r\n- Hero levels and skills.<br />\r\n- Customer jokes.<br />\r\n- The Board on which you leave orders.<br />\r\n- Fishing, you can not buy food, eat fish.<br />\r\n- Sandbox mode to the story.",
